oor. ', 'ferrino, shaba, tent, shaba tent, comfortable tent, camping tent', 3, '2018-01-26 22:44:24'),
(30, 'Ferrino Lightent  Tent 1 FR Red', '91144CRFR', '<p>A real example of light weight and reliability. Equipped with two pre-formed poles in duraluminium to increase the living space in the inner tent.</p>', '<p>A real example of light weight and reliability. Equipped with two pre-formed poles in duraluminium to increase the living space in the inner tent.</p>\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Color: </strong> Red</p>\r\n<p><strong>Maximum Weight: </strong> 1450 grams</p>\r\n<p><strong>Minimum Weight: </strong> 1300 grams</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong> 13x33 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Capacity: </strong> 1 person</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Fabrics</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Fly sheet in thermal insulating, aluminised Ripstop Polyester, waterproof to 3,000mm</li>\r\n  <li>Floor in thermal insulating aluminised waterproof polyester to 3,000mm</li>\r\n  <li>Mosquito net inner</li>\r\n  <li>Taped seams on fly sheet and floor</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Structure</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>2 shock-corded poles in duraluminium</li>\r\n  <li>Inner tent with continuous overhanging sleeves</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Entrance and Ventilation</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Mosquito net door</li>\r\n  <li>Ventilation outlets</li>\r\n  <li>“Air” ventilation system</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Accessories</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Quick adjusting guy lines</li>\r\n  <li>Inside storage pockets</li>\r\n  <li>Lamp hook</li>\r\n  <li>Stuff sack</li>\r\n  <li>Repair kit</li>\r\n  <li>Aluminium pegs</li>\r\n</ul>', '8800.00', 2, 'assets/img/products/ferrino-lightent--tent-1-fr-red.jpg', 'Ferrino Lightent  Tent 1 FR Red', 'Ferrino Lightent  Tent 1 FR Red is a real example of light weight and reliability. ', 'ferrino, tent, lightweight tent, lightent, lightent 1', 3, '2018-01-26 22:53:30'),
(31, 'Ferrino Sintesi 1 Olive Green', '91174DVO', '<p>Ferrino proposes a new series of 1 and 2 person tents intended for users requiring an ultra light tent with no compromises.</p>', '<p>Ferrino proposes a new series of 1 and 2 person tents intended for users requiring an ultra light tent with no compromises.</p>\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Color: </strong> Olive Green</p>\r\n<p><strong>Maximum Weight: </strong> 990 grams</p>\r\n<p><strong>Minimum Weight: </strong> 830 grams</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong> 14x30 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Capacity: </strong> 1 person</p>\r\n', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Fabrics</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Single walled tent in Ripstop 50D 3000 mm polyester FR treatment with mosquito net inside FR treated.</li>\r\n  <li>Floor in waterproof polyester &#40;3000 mm&#41; with FR treatment</li>\r\n  <li>Taped seams on fly-sheet and floor</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Structure</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Exernal poles</li>\r\n  <li>3 pre-formed duraluminium poles in different colours for easy setup</li>\r\n  <li>Exagon aluminium pegs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Entrance and Ventilation</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Mosquito net door</li>\r\n  <li>Vestibule</li>\r\n  <li>Front ventilation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Accessories</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>F.A. guy line</li>\r\n  <li>Inside storage pockets</li>\r\n  <li>Lamp hook</li>\r\n  <li>Stuff sack</li>\r\n  <li>Repair kit</li>\r\n</ul>', '8100.00', 3, 'assets/img/products/ferrino-sintesi-1-olive-green.jpg', 'Ferrino Sintesi 1 Olive Green', 'Ferrino Sintesi 1 Olive Green is intended for users requiring an ultra light tent with no compromises.</p>', 'ferrino sintersi 1, light tent, tent sintesi tent, camping tent', 3, '2018-01-26 22:59:41'),
(32, 'Ferrino Leaf 2 Lightweight Tent', '91196', '<p>Tent designed for those needing a lightweight tent for backpacking. Light, robust, and comfy, thanks to the innovative shape that increases living space around the inner tent ridge</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Color: </strong> Orange</p>\r\n<p><strong>Maximum Weight: </strong> 2500 grams</p>\r\n<p><strong>Minimum Weight: </strong> 2350 grams</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong> 15x43 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Capacity: </strong> 2 persons</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Fabrics</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Fly-sheet in Ripstop polyester &#40;3000 mm&#41; with FR treatment</li>\r\n  <li>Inner tent in mosquito net and polyester ripstop 70D fabric with FR treatment</li>\r\n  <li>Floor in FR polyester, waterproof to 3000 mm</li>\r\n  <li>Taped seams on fly-sheet and floor </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Structure</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>3 pre-formed duraluminium poles in different colours for easy setup</li>\r\n  <li>Inner tent overhung on poles with hooks for quick set-up</li>\r\n  <li>“Hexagon” aluminium pegs </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Entrance and Ventilation</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Vestibules</li>\r\n  <li>Mosquito net doors </li>\r\n  <li>Ventilation outlets </li>\r\n  <li>“Camera air” ventilation system </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Accessories</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>F.A. guy line</li>\r\n  <li>Inside storage pockets</li>\r\n  <li>“Ambient light” inner pockets</li>\r\n  <li>Lamp hook</li>\r\n  <li>Stuff sack</li>\r\n  <li>Repair kit</li>\r\n</ul>', '13300.00', 1, 'assets/img/products/ferrino-leaf-2-lightweight-tent.jpg', 'Ferrino Leaf 2 Lightweight Tent', 'Ferrino Leaf 2 Lightweight Tent is designed for those needing a lightweight tent for backpacking. ', 'ferrino, tent, lightweight tent, leaf tent', 3, '2018-01-26 23:10:09'),
(33, 'Ferrino Phantom 2 Tent', '91172BBB', '<p>Line of light tents for two or three persons which guarantee excellent living space and ventilation because of the duraluminium structure with ridge pole and double entrance with front and back vestibules.</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Color: </strong> Blue</p>\r\n<p><strong>Maximum Weight: </strong> 2300 grams</p>\r\n<p><strong>Minimum Weight: </strong> 2100 grams</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong> 14x36 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Capacity: </strong> 2 persons</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Fabrics</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Fly-sheet in Ripstop polyester &#40;3000 mm&#41; with FR treatment</li>\r\n  <li>Inner tent in FR mosquito net</li>\r\n  <li>Floor in FR polyester, waterproof to 3000 mm</li>\r\n  <li>Taped seams on fly-sheet and floor </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Structure</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>3 pre-formed duraluminium poles in different colours for easy setup</li>\r\n  <li>Inner tent overhung on poles with hooks</li>\r\n  <li>Exagon aluminium pegs </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Entrance and Ventilation</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Vestibules</li>\r\n  <li>Doors with external mosquito net, which open fully can be stored in the special pocket</li>\r\n  <li>Ventilation outlets </li>\r\n  <li>Air ventilation system for inner tent</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Accessories</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>F.A. guy line</li>\r\n  <li>Inside storage pockets</li>\r\n  <li>Lamp hook</li>\r\n  <li>Stuff sack</li>\r\n  <li>Repair kit</li>\r\n</ul>', '12200.00', 2, 'assets/img/products/ferrino-phantom-2-tent.jpg', 'Ferrino Phantom 2 Tent', 'Ferrino Phantom 2 Tent is a line of light tents for two or three persons which guarantee excellent living space and ventilation.', 'ferrino, phantom, phantom 2, tent, phantom 2 tent', 3, '2018-01-26 23:16:09');
