(35, 'Ferrino Lightent 2 Tent - Olive Green', '91145WMFR', '<p>A real example of light weight and reliability. Equipped with two pre-formed poles in duraluminium to increase the living space in the inner tent.</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Color: </strong> Olive Green</p>\r\n<p><strong>Maximum Weight: </strong> 1850 grams</p>\r\n<p><strong>Minimum Weight: </strong> 1650 grams</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong> 17x35 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Capacity: </strong> 2 persons</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Fabrics</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Fly sheet in thermal insulating, aluminised Ripstop Polyester, waterproof to 3,000mm</li>\r\n  <li>Floor in thermal insulating aluminised waterproof polyester to 3,000mm</li>\r\n  <li>Mosquito net inner</li>\r\n  <li>Taped seams on fly sheet and floor</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Structure</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>2 shock-corded poles in duraluminium</li>\r\n  <li>Inner tent with continuous overhanging sleeves</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Entrance and Ventilation</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Mosquito net door</li>\r\n  <li>Ventilation outlets</li>\r\n  <li>“Air” ventilation system</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Accessories</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Quick adjusting guy lines</li>\r\n  <li>Inside storage pockets</li>\r\n  <li>Lamp hook</li>\r\n  <li>Stuff sack</li>\r\n  <li>Repair kit</li>\r\n  <li>Aluminium pegs</li>\r\n</ul>', '11100.00', 2, 'assets/img/products/ferrino-lightent-2-tent-olive-green.jpg\r\n', 'Ferrino Lightent 2 Tent - Olive Green', 'Ferrino Lightent 2 Tent - olive green is a real example of light weight and reliability. ', 'ferrino, lightent, lightent 2, light tent', 3, '2018-01-26 23:28:58'),
(36, 'Ferrino Bivy High Lab Tent', '99078', '<p>The Bivy HL tent is a single-canvas, ultra-light and compact bivy tent.</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Color: </strong> Orange</p>\r\n<p><strong>Maximum Weight: </strong> 1250 grams</p>\r\n<p><strong>Minimum Weight: </strong> 1100 grams</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong> 11x35 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Capacity: </strong> 1 persons</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Fabrics</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Texit membrane waterproof to 4,000mm</li>\r\n  <li>Polyester floor waterproof to 8,000mm</li>\r\n  <li>Taped seams on fly sheet and floor</li>\r\n  <li>Triple reinforcement at floor corners</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Structure</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>2 shock-corded poles in duraluminium</li>\r\n  <li>Fly sheet suspended from external poles with sleeves</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Entrance and Ventilation</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Front entrance</li>\r\n  <li>Front door with internal mosquito net</li>\r\n  <li>Stormproof ventilation outlets</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Accessories</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Reflective quick adjusting guy lines</li>\r\n  <li>Stuff sack</li>\r\n  <li>Repair kit</li>\r\n  <li>Aluminium pegs</li>\r\n</ul>', '14900.00', 1, 'assets/img/products/ferrino-bivy-high-lab-tent.jpg', 'Ferrino Bivy High Lab Tent', 'Ferrino bivy high lab tent is a single-canvas, ultra-light and compact bivy tent.', 'ferrino, high lab tent, bivy, tent, lightweight tent', 3, '2018-01-26 23:36:13'),
(37, 'Ferrino Emperor 2 Tent', '99079', '<p>Emperor is the new frontier when it comes to the technology and performance achieved by Ferrino: the W.T.S. welding system is now used on expedition tents.</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Color: </strong> Orange</p>\r\n<p><strong>Maximum Weight: </strong> 3100 grams</p>\r\n<p><strong>Minimum Weight: </strong> 2800 grams</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong> 18x40 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Capacity: </strong> 2 persons</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Fabrics</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Fly-sheet in TU laminated 40D x 40D 254T nylon, waterproof to 10,000mm</li>\r\n  <li>Inner tent in water-repellent and breathable Ripstop polyester</li>\r\n  <li>Floor in waterproof polyester</li>\r\n  <li>Polyurethane front window</li>\r\n  <li>Taped seams on floor</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Structure</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Single support frame with shock-corded aluminium poles and radial joints</li>\r\n  <li>Inner tent overhung on poles with hooks</li>\r\n  <li>Aluminium pegs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Entrance and Ventilation</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>2 vestibules</li>\r\n  <li>2 fully opening door</li>\r\n  <li>Ventilation outlets</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Accessories</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Lamp hook</li>\r\n  <li>Quick adjusting guy lines</li>\r\n  <li>Repair kit</li>\r\n  <li>Compact stuff sack</li>\r\n</ul>', '31000.00', 3, 'assets/img/products/ferrino-emperor-2-tent.jpg', 'Ferrino Emperor 2 Tent', 'Ferrino Emperor 2 Tent is the new frontier when it comes to the technology and performance achieved by Ferrino: the W.T.S. welding system is now used on expedition tents.', 'ferrino, emperor, emperor 2, tent, camping tent', 3, '2018-01-26 23:44:41'),
(38, 'Ferrino Nemesi 1 Tent', '91166', '<p>A range of super-light tents made using FR fabrics, with solidarised duraluminium structure with radial joints and ridge pole to guarantee excellent comfort and easy set up.</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Maximum Weight: </strong> 1700 grams</p>\r\n<p><strong>Minimum Weight: </strong> 1500 grams</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong> 13x34 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Capacity: </strong> 1 person</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Fabrics</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Fly-sheet in Ripstop polyester &#40;3000 mm&#41; </li>\r\n  <li>Inner tent in FR mosquito net </li>\r\n  <li>Floor in FR polyester, waterproof to 3000 mm </li>\r\n  <li>Taped seams on fly-sheet and floor </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Structure</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Supporting structure with shock-corded duraluminium poles and radial joint</li>\r\n  <li>Duraluminium ridge pole in a different colour</li>\r\n  <li>Inner tent overhung on poles with hooks </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Entrance and Ventilation</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Vestibule </li>\r\n  <li>Fully opening mosquito net doors </li>\r\n  <li>Ventilation outlets</li>\r\n  <li>“Camera Air” ventilation system </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Accessories</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>F.A. guy line adjustment </li>\r\n  <li>Inside storage pockets</li>\r\n  <li>Lamp hook </li>\r\n  <li>Stuff sack </li>\r\n  <li>Repair kit </li>\r\n</ul>', '10000.00', 1, 'assets/img/products/ferrino-nemesi-1-tent.jpg', 'Ferrino Nemesi 1 Tent', 'A range of super-light tents made using FR fabrics, with solidarised duraluminium structure with radial joints and ridge pole to guarantee excellent comfort and easy set up.', 'ferrino, light tent, nemesi, nemesi 1', 3, '2018-01-26 23:52:05');

